{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_14_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 ドキドキさせてやるんだから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、ミーティングを始めるわね\nこれが、私が書いたもし恋のアンケートよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 133.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 4.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私が思う理想の恋愛のシチュエーションを書いたけど\nこれでときめくか、意見を聞かせてちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。では、具体的に\nどんなことを書いたのか教えてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1006768718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、口頭で説明するの？　私の理想の恋を声に出して\n説明するのは、恥ずかしくて抵抗があるんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに重く考えずに、気楽にいきましょう\nどうせアンケートは他の人達も読むんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれないけど……\nああもう、分かったわよ。説明すればいいんでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 43.4666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私がときめくと思う恋のシチュエーションは\n競い合い共に切磋琢磨するライバルとの恋愛よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームの中の私は、陸上部に所属する高校生で\n部内には一緒に頑張る気の置けない友達がいるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 61.3999997456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "その友達とはいつも衝突して口喧嘩ばかりするけど\n本心ではお互いをリスペクトして認め合っているのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.733333079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "練習が終わると一緒に下校して、夕焼けが綺麗な\n海岸通りを歩いて……喧嘩して、夢を語り合って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.5000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.4333320617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな身近な存在を、ふとしたきっかけで意識する\nようになって、この気持ちは友情？　それとも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.466665395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "熱く語っているところをすみません\n莉央さん、そのアンケート、全部書き直しです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 93.600004832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてよ！\n私の理想の恋愛じゃときめかないって言うの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0666730245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなくて、今回は大人の恋愛がテーマなので\n高校生の設定は使えないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2000063579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにゲームには莉央さん本人が出演するんですよ？\n莉央さんが女子高生に扮するのは、ちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3901361499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.3000094096
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "私に女子高生役は無理だって言いたいの？\n私の制服姿は痛々しいって言いたいの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333442688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺はそこまで言ってません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5666760762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.7666760762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "全部書き直しだなんて……一人で部屋にこもって\n深夜まで悩んで書いたのに、苦労が全部水の泡だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8819062126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 133.9333396911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、大人の恋愛なんてどう書けばいいのよ\n考え方があるなら教えてほしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6000078837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.1666730244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……例えば、アイドルをやっていなかったら\nどんな大人になっていたか想像してみるのはどうですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8666745503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.7000063578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルにならなかったら？　……うちは母子家庭で\nあまり裕福じゃないから、きっと就職していたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1666745503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 158.1666730244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "就職ですか、莉央さんはスーツ姿が似合いそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.1666730244,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "スーツが似合うオフィスワーカー……。バリバリ働いて\nビジネスパーソンとして活躍する人生も悪くないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3666745503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.6000063578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、仕事が忙しいと恋愛するのは難しそうだわ\n仕事人間がどうやって恋の相手と出会うのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.3999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 181.1000063578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、相手は会社の同僚じゃないですか？\n莉央さんなら年下の後輩から慕われそうな気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.8000078837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 188.6333396911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
