      "text": "それで付き合い始めるけど、周りに知られるのは\n恥ずかしいから、みんなには内緒で社内恋愛を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.6333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "こっそり待ち合わせしたり、秘密のやりとりをしたり\n残業で二人きりになってここぞとばかりに甘えたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.7930011723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 216.9666730244
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "いいわ、イメージがどんどん膨らんできた\n一人で悩んでいた時はあんなに苦労したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.0999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 224.8000053405
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "貴方と話すとアイデアがすらすら思い浮かぶわ\nそれだけ私のことを理解してくれているってことかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.5666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺は莉央さんのマネージャーですから。莉央さんの\nことなら誰よりもよく分かっているつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.800017039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
