      "text": "恋愛ゲームのヒロインがこれでいいのかしら\nこんな女性、誰も好きにならないんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.9333452861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 303.0333447774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_14_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "高い目標を持って仕事に真剣に打ち込む人は素敵です\n俺はそういう女性、好きですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.5000200908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
